LibMsgque Test Environment
==========================


The scripts used in this directory are used to verify the libmsgque
library inclusing the tcl, java and python language binding. 
Testing is done using the tcltest feature of the tcl distribution.
The tests are done using 3 different approaches:

  1. using the test feature of the build environment
	> make check (not available for windows)

  2. invoke an individual test script
	> tclsh tests/int.test (example)

  3. invoke all tests
	> tclsh tests/all.tcl

  4. example: invoke all tests but only using the "python" interpreter
	> tclsh tests/all.tcl --only-python

  5. example: invoke all tests but only using the "tcp/ip" server
	> tclsh tests/all.tcl --only-tcp

Help is available with the following commands:

  1. test specific help
	> tclsh tests/all.tcl --help

  2. tcltest specific help
	> man tcltest

